orkspace files by glob pattern, sorted newest-first | Locate files when you know the name pattern but not the exact path (e.g. `*.json`, `**/findings-*.txt`). Sorted by mtime descending so the most-recently-written hits come first. |
| **fs_find** | Metadata-based file search (name pattern + mtime + size + type filters) | When glob alone is not enough - filter by recency (mtime=<1h), size (size=>10M), or type (file/dir/symlink). |
| **fs_list** | Single-directory listing with type indicator, size, mtime | Look inside one specific directory. Use fs_tree for a hierarchical view, fs_glob/fs_find for pattern-based search. |
